    <Text name="4. Counter measures" LabelPosition="Middle" Note="&lt;div&gt;We can take several countermeasures to either slow or stop the spread of the virus. These policy measures are in modelled in &lt;b&gt;yellow &lt;/b&gt;in the model&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Minimize contacts between people by working from home, closing schools, daycares and shops. Asking people to keep good hand hygien and keep distances in public&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stop or minimize travel cross borders&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Vaccinate people once vaccine is available&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" id="52">
      <mxCell style="text;fontSize=24;fontFamily=Verdana;" parent="1" vertex="1">
        <mxGeometry x="1140" y="590" width="380" height="50" as="geometry" />
      </mxCell>
    </Text>
